subsection.def:
animal
                    (動物) has the meaning given by section
                    2(1) of the Public Health and Municipal Services Ordinance (Cap. 132);

Director
                    (署長) means the Director of Food and
                Environmental Hygiene;

export
                    (出口) means to take out or cause to be taken
                out of Hong Kong by air, land or water;

import
                    (進口) means to bring or cause to be brought
                into Hong Kong by air, land or water;

premises
                    (處所) has the meaning given by section
                    2(1) of the Public Health and Municipal Services Ordinance (Cap. 132);
